   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1656_dai_lns235ms_d_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                     <gap/>
                      خان مرید
                     <gap/>
                     <persName ref="#shahJahan">شاه جهان</persName>
                  </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
                     <gap/>
                      Khan disciple of
                     <gap/>
                     <persName ref="#shahJahan">Shah Jahan</persName>
                  </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p><lb/>چودهریان و زمینداران و قانونگویان و مقدمان و رعایا و مزارعان پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               <lb/>از صوبه
               <placeName ref="#malwa">مالوه</placeName>
                بدانند که چون درین سال بعنایت الهی و مناقب اقبال لایزال شاهی
               <lb/>باران رحمت ایزدی از اول تا آخر موافق مدعا نازل شده و خوبیهای زراعات بکمال
               <lb/>رسیده و باران آخر برای زراعت ربیع آب حیات بوده امسال سال کامل بلکه
               <lb/>اکمل است و احدی را جای سخن نمانده و عین وقت مالگذاری فصلخریف
               <gap/>
                و تردد زراعت
               <lb/>ربیع همینست باید که بخاطر جمع در ادای مالواجبی از قرار واقع و تردد زراعت ربیع و
               افزونی
               <lb/>آبادانی و معموری پرگنه مذکور آنچنان سعی و کوشش نماید که مجری دولتخواهی و آبادان
               کاری
               <lb/>آنها بظهور آمد که در خور آن رعایت خواهند یافت درین باب قدغن تمام لازم دانسته
               <lb/>حسب المسطور بعمل آرند تحریر التاریخ
               <date calendar="#julus">
                  <num>۱٥</num>
                   شهر صفر سنه
                  <num>٣۰</num>
               </date>
                از جلوس مبارک 
                <g ref="#baiz">بیضه</g> </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">Chaudhris</ref> and <ref type="glossary"
                  target="#gl_zamindar">zamindars</ref> and <ref type="glossary"
                  target="#gl_qanungo">qanungos</ref> and peasants and agriculturists of <ref
                  type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>
               <lb/>of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_suba">suba</ref>
               <placeName ref="#malwa">Malwa</placeName>, should know that since in this year, by divine favour and the infinite imperial
               glorious virtues,
               <lb/>the rain of compassion of God from beginning to end has fallen as planned, the
               excellence of cultivation
               <lb/>has reached perfection, and the last rains have been the the water of life for
               the spring harvest; [so] this year is a perfect year - nay,
               <lb/>the most perfect year.
               <note>By "perfect year," the writer suggests that because of the fullness of the
                  rains, it is a year in which the full tax demand should be paid.</note>
                And no one has any place to say anything, and the opportune moment of the payment of taxes of the autumn
               harvest
               <gap/>
                is the same as [making] efforts for the cultivation of
               <lb/>the spring [crop]. With peace of mind, make such efforts towards the
               payment of taxes, which have been settled, and the cultivation of the spring crop and
               enhancement of
               <lb/>the population and cultivation of the aforementioned <ref type="glossary"
                  target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> that [these] efforts and exertions reveal what
               they [the officials addressed in the letter] who cause the population and cultivation
               <lb/>have manifested; [and] in fulfillment of that, they will be favoured. Knowing
               that all legitimate prohibitions are applicable in this matter,
               <lb/>execute as written. Written on
               <date calendar="#julus">15 of the month of Safar in year 30 of the blessed
                  reign</date>. <g ref="#baiz">Ended</g>. </p>
         </div>

         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1656_dai_lns235ms_d_v.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
            <p> <unclear>بتاریخ</unclear>
               <date calendar="#julus"><unclear><num>۱۶</num></unclear>
               شهر صفر سنه
               <num>٣۰</num></date>
                نقل
               <unclear>سیاهه</unclear>
                حضور
               <unclear>شد</unclear>
               <gap></gap>
               د
            </p>
         </div>

         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p>
               <unclear>On the date of</unclear>
                16 of the month of Safar in the year 30, a copy
                [reached the] <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_siyahaHuzur">siyaha huzur</ref><gap></gap><note>The meaning of the letter underneath this note is unclear.</note></p>
         </div>

